{"tid":2464173,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"僅 6.6% 人已打首劑疫苗　林鄭：料長時間達群體免疫　研以「出行便利」鼓勵接種","createTime":"2021-03-27T09:13:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-27T09:43:52.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8f17baf6464f20a3075db4c0cafe1301cce714ab","tid":2464173,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T09:13:43.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫苗接種計劃展開一個月，特首林鄭月娥今日（27 日）發表第 14 個月抗疫報告，指截至昨日有 43 萬人已打首劑疫苗，佔 16 歲或以上「合資格接種」市民的 6.6%。林鄭稱，必須要有相當比例市民接種疫苗，才能達至「群體免疫」，「以現時的接種率，恐怕要一段頗長時間方能達成目標。」<br />\n<br />\n為鼓勵市民接種疫苗，她表示當局正考慮若一定數目市民接種疫苗，可以進一步調整社交距離措施，並與其他地區商討，為已接種疫苗的旅客提供「出行便利」。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥指，近日有少量復必泰疫苗有包裝瑕疵，但不影響疫苗安全，政府已應藥廠要求暫停為市民接種復必泰疫苗，「反映我們是十分謹慎，亦是以市民健康為首要考慮。」<br />\n<br />\n談到近月疫情，林鄭月娥稱過去一月的「食肆群組」及「健身室群組」，令確診個案出現兩個「小高峰」，但根據港大團隊分析，有關個案是第四波疫情延續，並沒有輸入個案，亦沒有變種病毒株流入社區。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%83%85-6-6-%E4%BA%BA%E5%B7%B2%E6%89%93%E9%A6%96%E5%8A%91%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD-%E6%96%99%E9%95%B7%E6%99%82%E9%96%93%E9%81%94%E7%BE%A4%E9%AB%94%E5%85%8D%E7%96%AB-%E7%A0%94%E4%BB%A5-%E5%87%BA%E8%A1%8C%E4%BE%BF%E5%88%A9-%E9%BC%93%E5%8B%B5%E6%8E%A5%E7%A8%AE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%2583%2585-6-6-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E6%2589%2593%25E9%25A6%2596%25E5%258A%2591%25E7%2596%25AB%25E8%258B%2597-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD-%25E6%2596%2599%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%2599%2582%25E9%2596%2593%25E9%2581%2594%25E7%25BE%25A4%25E9%25AB%2594%25E5%2585%258D%25E7%2596%25AB-%25E7%25A0%2594%25E4%25BB%25A5-%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%25A1%258C%25E4%25BE%25BF%25E5%2588%25A9-%25E9%25BC%2593%25E5%258B%25B5%25E6%258E%25A5%25E7%25A8%25AE%2F&d=jrWVSpMJYTM9%2F%2BTkK0Hr34%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=6d073877\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%2583%2585-6-6-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E6%2589%2593%25E9%25A6%2596%25E5%258A%2591%25E7%2596%25AB%25E8%258B%2597-%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD-%25E6%2596%2599%25E9%2595%25B7%25E6%2599%2582%25E9%2596%2593%25E9%2581%2594%25E7%25BE%25A4%25E9%25AB%2594%25E5%2585%258D%25E7%2596%25AB-%25E7%25A0%2594%25E4%25BB%25A5-%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%25A1%258C%25E4%25BE%25BF%25E5%2588%25A9-%25E9%25BC%2593%25E5%258B%25B5%25E6%258E%25A5%25E7%25A8%25AE%2F&h=873a9e3c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%83%85-6-6-%E4%BA%BA%E5%B7%B2%E6%89%93%E9%A6%96%E5%8A%91%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD-%E6%96%99%E9%95%B7%E6%99%82%E9%96%93%E9%81%94%E7%BE%A4%E9%AB%94%E5%85%8D%E7%96%AB-%E7%A0%94%E4%BB%A5-%E5%87%BA%E8%A1%8C%E4%BE%BF%E5%88%A9-%E9%BC%93%E5%8B%B5%E6%8E%A5%E7%A8%AE/</a>"},{"pid":"cfb738032e1c91f9863dd57b1b2a429be8186421","tid":2464173,"uid":200663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T09:14:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYXa7WGGZhXkQU9d7a5RQPMPfBcnAKHyJ8rpNqwoZBdCT?filename=jD4y2es.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjD4y2es.png&h=c19073d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e9d9b300037c3e447d5effb8e3c4676502e23a17","tid":2464173,"uid":54721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T09:14:35.000Z","msg":"即係準備罰唔打既人"},{"pid":"d8d5e4b2f46097590fc188f0694343f812cd07a7","tid":2464173,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T09:15:58.000Z","msg":"就算全港的人都打科興都唔駛旨意群體免疫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf72fde67d9610fd9d7232fe9d79d34c5c986923","tid":2464173,"uid":205099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T09:24:46.000Z","msg":"3萬隻狗同班家屬幾時去打啊屌你老母又話忠誠勇毅，打支科興就縮返入老母個閪到"},{"pid":"ab1738ae7ed160300d48f7e8ee95371f16661762","tid":2464173,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T09:35:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span class=\"red\">並與其他地區商討，為已接種疫苗的旅客提供「出行便利」</span></blockquote>打完科興只可以去非洲国家同埋支那，明架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其他國家根本唔認科興"},{"pid":"7c02668fafb5a5f4f2abf27ffb6ba2f911df422a","tid":2464173,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T09:37:19.000Z","msg":"無人認可針廢物，睇下智利就知<br />\n<br />\n同埋就算Biontech都無人知有幾耐效力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0de476a9515fbd24bff0632a40fe25d550f31c5","tid":2464173,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9d9b300037c3e447d5effb8e3c4676502e23a17","tid":2464173,"uid":54721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T09:14:35.000Z","msg":"即係準備罰唔打既人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T09:43:52.000Z","msg":"安心出殯都迫唔到<br />\n就睇點迫人打毒針<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時個個都有長期病患<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}